186
00:29:21,710 --> 00:29:26,010
你真漂亮，今天想干什么？
you look beautiful. What are you gonna do today?

187
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:28,510
没什么特别的
Nothing in particular.

188
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:32,310
