- If you want me to.  - Thank you, darling.

191
00:29:40,440 --> 00:29:42,480
走这儿
There.

192
00:29:42,730 --> 00:29:47,910
- 你可真快  - 是的，先生
- you're very quick.  - That I am, sir.

193
00:30:19,270 --> 00:30:21,690
对不起，夫人
Excuse me, ma'am.

194
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:33,120
别叫，嗨
Quiet. Hey.

195
00:30:36,790 --> 00:30:39,210
趴下
Lie down.

196
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:49,430
- 你好  - 你好
- Hello.  - Hello.

197
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:54,640
- 有什么事吗？ - 先生想知道你什么时候让鸡孵蛋？
- What can I do for you?  - When will you set the eggs?

198
00:30:54,890 --> 00:31:00,270
