Only, why doesn't Sir Clifford build a little summerhouse for you?

207
00:32:06,790 --> 00:32:09,340
不用，我就是想看鸡孵蛋
No, I want to watch the pheasants.

208
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:13,550
