Don't make a key. On second thought, I don't ever want to be here again.

212
00:32:38,330 --> 00:32:42,710
克利夫德？把你的话传达给迈勒斯了，这是什么？
Clifford? I gave Mellors your message. What's this?

213
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:47,290
我决定再磨炼一下自己的手，想起雷诺阿了
I've decided to try my hand again, thinking of Renoir.

214
00:32:47,540 --> 00:32:52,260
- 真是个好主意  - 没错，我以前一直画得不太好
- What a good idea.  - Of course, I was never very good.

215
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:55,590
不知道会画成什么样，反正已经开始了
I wonder what I'll see now, after all that's happened.

216
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:59,760
- 给我画幅像吧  - 那你得排队等着
- Well, there's always me.  - you'll have to join the queue.

217
00:33:00,010 --> 00:33:03,140
