219
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:10,860
没有，她只是想让你更自由一些
No, she just thought it would free you more.

220
00:33:11,110 --> 00:33:14,610
她要给我做康复，所以要住下
She'll give me my exercises. She may as well be here.

221
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:19,160
- 这样不是很好吗？ - 是很好
- It's marvellous, isn't it?  - Marvellous.

222
00:33:20,910 --> 00:33:24,210
伯尔顿太太，你要和我们住上一阵，这太好了
you'll be staying with us a while. That's good.

223
00:33:24,460 --> 00:33:28,750
我觉得这样最好，你今天找到迈勒斯先生了吗？
I think it's for the best. Did you find Mr. Mellors today?

224
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:33,170
找到了，他是我见过的最没礼貌的人
I did. He's the most insolent man I've ever talked to.

225
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:37,260
他从小就是个目中无人的小坏蛋
He was a defiant little demon, even when he was a lad.

226
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:43,180
