you can't do that. you're cheating.

232
00:33:57,410 --> 00:34:02,330
那是你的，该我了，我出J
That's you. My go. Jack.

233
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:08,170
- 换牌  - 我累了，我想上楼了
- Card change.  - I'm tired. I think I'll go up.

234
00:34:08,420 --> 00:34:10,250
- 晚安，伯尔顿太太  - 晚安，去人
- Good night.  - Good night.

235
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:13,800
- 晚安，亲爱的  - 晚安
- Good night, darling.  - Good night.

236
00:34:16,510 --> 00:34:20,260
- 我出十  - 十
- Ten.  - Ten.

237
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:24,270
- 八，换牌  - 换同花？
- Eight and change.  - Change of suit?

238
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:25,890
- 是的  - 要哪个花色？
- yes.  - To what?

239
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:29,850
- 梅花  - 给你梅花
- Clubs.  - Clubs.

240
00:34:35,690 --> 00:34:39,700
克利夫德，我有个问题，你说了我应该找个情人
Clifford, I have a problem. you said I should take a lover.

241
00:34:39,950 --> 00:34:46,290
- 想让我帮你挑吗？ - 不是，如果有了孩子怎么办？
- Want me to choose for you, do you?  - No, but what if I have a child?

