Couldn't you promise it'd be by the Holy Ghost?

245
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:59,340
- 你会介意吗？ - 谁的孩子？
- Would you mind?  - Whose child?

246
00:34:59,970 --> 00:35:01,590
但是你会问？
But need you ask?

247
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:05,970
是不是别人会那样看，孩子是圣灵的？
Isn't it the Holy Ghost if one looks at it that way?

248
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:11,150
好吧，亲爱的，生育是自然法则
All right, my dear, breed. It's nature's law.

249
00:35:11,350 --> 00:35:15,940
我相信我的儿子，他的父亲配得上准男爵
I trust my son and heir will have a father worthy of a baronet.

250
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:18,320
当然，我相信你的品味
But I trust your taste.

251
00:35:26,790 --> 00:35:32,630
- 这对你们俩都是一种牺牲  - 为什么而牺牲？
