I haven't got the hang of it this way.

265
00:36:56,750 --> 00:37:00,210
我要是能赢，那就是风向变了
Well, it'll be a change for me to win.

266
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:05,340
听说你今天做了件和你性格不太相符的事
I hear you did something rather out of character today.

267
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:08,800
- 去教堂了，是吗？ - 是的
