277
00:38:00,270 --> 00:38:03,190
- 没有，一点都不晚  - 睡得好吗，夫人？
- Not at all.  - Did you sleep well, milady?

278
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:07,360
谢谢，伯尔顿太太，我去吃早餐了
Thank you, Mrs. Bolton. Well, I'll have some breakfast.

279
00:38:07,610 --> 00:38:09,410
